    MetaModelInfoProvider
    public static class MetaModelInfoProvider.StuffedMetaModelInfo
extends MetaModelInfoProvider.BaseMetaModelInfo
    Provider which is filled with desired information. Queries, if could not be resolved with the information filled in, are directed to delegate. Depending on actual delegate used, may answer null.

    • Method Detail

      • populate

        public void populate​(@NotNull
                     MetaModelInfoProvider.StuffedMetaModelInfo other)
        Fill another StuffedMetaModelInfo instance with information known to this one. It might be necessary if we don't want to use this provider as is due to delegate.

        There would be no need in this method if we could pass proper StuffedMetaModelInfo instance right into modelFactory.load(). However, given Map(String,String) for options, we have to assume there might be inappropriate delegate which we can't rely on (i.e. merge has to combine few stuffed sources, asks them one by one, first one to answer wins)
